title: Inside a Game
tags: 2012 Atari dance DHS Falcon synthpop video
info:
All sound goes from Atari Falcon 030 (stock version). 
It's a 10-channels song made on DHS-Tracker (Digital Home Studio).

Computers used: 
Atari Falcon 030 (main work and everything - almost ;) ),
Atari 520ST (for samples),
ZX Spectrum 48K with AY-interface (for samples).

Synthesizers used for samples: 
Yamaha E423

Software: 
Main editor - on Falcon - DHS-Tracker (Digital Home Studio)
MusicMon V2.5e on Atari 520ST (samples-making)
SoundTracker 1.1 on ZX Spectrum 48K (samples-making).

This is my third Falcon song. It took the first place on digital music contest of SillyVenture 2012 party.
